        "subject": "VoomLux — we got your request 🖤",
        "emailFormat": "text",
        "text": "=Hi {{ $json.name || 'there' }},\n\nThanks for reaching out to VoomLux. We received your request{{ $json.service_type && $json.service_type !== 'other' ? ' for ' + $json.service_type + ' service' : '' }} and a member of our team is reviewing it right now.\n\nYou'll hear from us shortly with availability and a flat-rate quote — no surge pricing, ever.\n\nNeed us faster? Just reply to this email.\n\n— The VoomLux Team\nLuxury black-SUV transportation · Philadelphia",
